media: rcar-csi2: Fix coccinelle warning for PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO()

Use the PTR_ERR_OR_ZERO() macro instead of construct:

    if (IS_ERR(foo))
        return PTR_ERR(foo);

    return 0;

Fixes: 3ae854cafd76 ("rcar-csi2: Use standby mode instead of resetting")

